(191, 19, 'Water Soluble', 'Water Soluble', NULL, '<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Buy Water-Soluble Fertilizer And Increase Growth Of Crops</strong></h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">AgriBegri&#39;s water-soluble fertilizers are an up-to-date technique for combining water and nourishment of your plants. These are the droppings that dissolve in water and become liquid for plants, providing more than just basic nutrients.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This method enables plants to be both watered and nourished at the same time. The method allows you to spend less time and effort at each individual watering &amp; fertilizing period and allows you to kill two birds with one stone.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">AgriBegri is a user-friendly marketplace that has all the necessary farming equipment. You can also find all the fertilizers on this platform. AgriBegri is an innovative online store that has a solution to all your needs.</p>', '<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Detail Information On Water Soluble Products</strong></h2><p dir=\"ltr\">Water-soluble fertilizers are like the lifeline of crops around the globe, as they help maintain the nutrient balance, which, in turn, provides healthy growth.</p><p dir=\"ltr\">These nutrients make the crop&#39;s health better. The primary macronutrients are nitrogen, phosphorus, and potassium, along with a few other micronutrients which are best for the crops.&nbsp;</p><p dir=\"ltr\">Farmers can apply water-soluble fertilizers to their crops in such a way that it is easy for crops to absorb the essential elements through water, which will result in better growth and higher crop yield.</p><p dir=\"ltr\">Remember to follow the recommended application measures when using this fertilizer. You need to dilute it in water according to the dosage instructions. After that, it is possible to directly spray it on the crops and/or soil using foliar products. According to your preference and the plants, the best way of irrigating would be via drip, soil, or <a href=\"https://vikaspedia.in/agric